@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vrowqx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (tmp + wp.sin(0.33))
    v2 = ((v0 - (v0 + 0.45 / v1 + 0.03)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.89) * (v1 + 0.02 * v0 + 0.96)))
    data[tid] = v0
